The paper discusses the use of different transmission methods and precoders for massive MIMO systems, which are typically studied in the fields of information theory (cs.IT), communication systems (cs.COMM), and signal processing (cs.SY). The focus on power efficiency and amplifier distortion also suggests relevance to the fields of networking and internet architecture (cs.NI) and multimedia (cs.MM).
